    <step order="7" name="Tests">Race tests: (a) clean update succeeds; (b) stale `expectedLastUserEditAt` refused with structured response; (c) null `expectedLastUserEditAt` permitted for agent-just-created tab. ADR-015 audit: `changes` body NEVER in telemetry.</step>
